definitions.definition: A maritime traditional county of Wales , bordered by Glamorganshire , Brecknockshire , Cardiganshire and Pembrokeshire .
A local government principal area, bordered by Swansea , Neath Port Talbot , Powys , Ceredigion and Pembrokeshire .
